item.title: A Deep Dive into Google Cloud's AlloyDB with Andi Gutmans| Cloud Wars Live
item.description: In this special episode of Cloud Wars Live, Bob Evans talks with Andi Gutmans, vice president and general manager, Google Cloud. They explore the transformative capabilities of AlloyDB, Google Cloud's fast-growing database offering and its role in meeting the demands of modern enterprises.
